><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Буйруқ рақами</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#4}Буйруқ қабул қилинган жой</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Болани овқатлантириш учун қўшимча </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">танаффус бериш ҳақида</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">1. </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#6}Ходимнинг иш жойи ва лавозими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#7}Ходимнинг Ф.И.Оси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">га</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> унинг икки ёшга тўлмаган боласи борлигини инобатга олиб, </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#8}Ходимга боласини овқатлантириш учун қўшимча танаффус берилиши бошланадиган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> кунидан дам олиш ва овқатланиш учун танаффусдан ташқари болани овқатлантириш учун қўшимча танаффус вақтлари берилсин.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Ходимга болани овқатлантириш учун бериладиган қўшимча танаффус вақтлари ҳар уч соат учун 30 дақиқадан иборат давомийликда берилсин.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">2. Ходимга қўлланилган мазкур имтиёз ходимнинг фарзанди 2 ёшга тўлгунига қадар – </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#9}Ушбу имтиёз амал қилиши тугатиладиган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> кунига қадар амал қилади.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">3. Болани овқатлантириш учун қўшимча танаффуслар иш вақтига киритилиши эътиборга олинсин, шу муносабат билан Бухгалтерия бўлими бу давр учун <span class=\"leading\"></span>ходимга ўртача иш ҳақи бўйича ҳақ тўланишини таъминласин.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 6pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Асос:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Меҳнат кодексининг 407-моддаси, ходимнинг аризаси ва боланинг туғилганлик ҳақидаги гувоҳномаси нусхаси.</span></p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#10}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг лавозими</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">_______________</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#11}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; d